description:
EARBUDi's clip on and off your original round iPod and iPhone earbuds. Keeps earbuds in your ears during any sporting activity or for general use. Turns your standard Apple earbuds into sport buds. 


iPod is a trademark of Apple, Inc., registered in the U.S. and other countries. iPhone is a trademark of Apple, Inc.
title: EARBUDi Clips on and off Your Apple iPod or iPhone Earbuds
